{"tid":427390,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日食譚仔冇帶錢，佢竟然畀左呢張野我簽","createTime":"2017-10-07T13:07:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T16:20:06.000Z","uid":61903,"like":1559,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"770f310c147f9332d5feba1a79943cf3dd578464","tid":427390,"uid":61903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:07:23.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇人一早已經知<br />\n話說今日自己一個食譚啦<br />\n食完譚仔先發現唔記得撳錢<br />\n埋單果時死死地氣咁問個收銀<br />\n可唔可以過隔離7仔撳畀你<br />\n佢話可以但你簽一簽呢張野先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ut8ghke3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fut8ghke3&h=a2d040a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我一望到成個人呆撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後面仲有兩三個人排緊隊等埋單<br />\n個個人望住我簽呢張回條 勁羞恥<br />\n到底邊個發明呢張野架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8eadfe8fa9bdd9cec5c34c52799e041d6f49999","tid":427390,"uid":28031,"like":798,"dislike":6,"score":792,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:11:14.000Z","msg":"人地報警拉你咪重柒"},{"pid":"4bd8ece3f275c14dab58866152fe847eac2047a0","tid":427390,"uid":6778,"like":504,"dislike":3,"score":501,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:12:42.000Z","msg":"你當人地開善堂？"},{"pid":"d04eb5cb586107619501bb0d2fae9cd3f9127ddb","tid":427390,"uid":61903,"like":7,"dislike":243,"score":-236,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:14:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你當人地開善堂？</blockquote><br />\n冇話咩既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n純粹覺得好搞笑<br />\n上面鳩寫佢都唔知啦"},{"pid":"2c56884ef5d01ce86069c61a7fae9d3a4360164c","tid":427390,"uid":125720,"like":5,"dislike":14,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:18:29.000Z","msg":"簽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a83d600f75bdb16b6854552ee89c594755d9ee","tid":427390,"uid":91982,"like":410,"dislike":0,"score":410,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:19:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2204fff62d5d0e74ab689aecd6deaeb041