","tid":427390,"uid":65468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:50:19.000Z","msg":"試過自己話放低張身分證俾佢<br />\n佢ok"},{"pid":"3ef3d399ae8c00ad6b8b6df6f70972000023662c","tid":427390,"uid":65468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:50:29.000Z","msg":"試過自己話放低張身分證俾佢<br />\n佢ok"},{"pid":"0ebbe81f7597c7e67ffa95e99bcdc704564781ac","tid":427390,"uid":63923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:26:26.000Z","msg":"好大個on9呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5307675d27b805f114bb2469f7a37fcc514c1b","tid":427390,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:32:35.000Z","msg":"樓豬應該幾樣衰下先幾十蚊都要簽呢d紙"},{"pid":"0bb977add74b5c97eb054065686441a6699f1550","tid":427390,"uid":148201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:39:30.000Z","msg":"我又係試過冇現金，又唔收八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要我去嗰陣係差唔多收鋪，食食下要我埋左單先，唯有打電話叫住附近fd借住錢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba315cb69d842d217430634cf0fecdf6a8ecc75e","tid":427390,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T18:45:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過自己話放低張身分證俾佢<br />\n佢ok</blockquote><br />\n我試過幾次。主動話放底身份證<br />\n未試過有一間要放底。<br />\n都係個句：&ldquo;幾十蚊方你會走咗去咩&rdquo;<br />\n㩒機俾返錢。都係話:哇。乜咁快呀。下次經過先吖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4d17634680f633a9668b99e3f873750de3deb2","tid":427390,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T20:23:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知有冇人一早已經知<br />\n話說今日自己一個食譚啦<br />\n食完譚仔先發現唔記得撳錢<br />\n埋單果時死死地氣咁問個收銀<br />\n可唔可以過隔離7仔撳畀你<br />\n佢話可以但你簽一簽呢張野先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ut8ghke3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fut8ghke3&h=a2d040a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我一望到成個人呆撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後面仲有兩三個人排緊隊等埋單<br />\n個個人望住我簽呢張<span style=\"color: red;\"> 回條</span>勁羞恥<br />\n到底邊個發明呢張野架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇間尺？借著比你先"},{"pid":"bd46d66e488314b9aab45e61392a554c977963eb","tid":427390,"uid":120801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T22:58:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今日食竟然見到咁嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d16838476f1688cf714eacf903635b604760939","tid":427390,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T23:32:54.000Z","msg":"我都試過冇錢喺身 好彩老板好人話信得過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87240bedbb233b809adb00dbc983591690dc1716","tid":427390,"uid":1714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T00:26:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>八達通都無？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n譚仔只能現金</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a98f98fbae5e43d75447b4852c5d1d11f554b7e","tid":427390,"uid":147445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T00:29:29.000Z","msg":"比完錢可唔可以拎返張野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f2127c3b09a1640d4771f72c3253f7c58703fb8","tid":427390,"uid":16084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T00:46:56.000Z","msg":"好耐冇見過回條呢隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3429de6ed079751b5b7ab4aa01b7673d76728bc2","tid":427390,"uid":61903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T00:57:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比完錢可唔可以拎返張野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以 我扔左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67b18c5b88c1c2b569afb9471f6de9cc820a73f","tid":427390,"uid":10342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T01:02:23.000Z","msg":"開張支票比佢收唔收<br />\n因為我都好少帶現金，多數八達通同信用卡及1-2張支票<br />\n<br />\n昨日食麥記點完餐，佢話只收現金我呆左呆，銀包得幾十蚊港幾同十幾蚊美金，好彩都夠港紙比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f1fb795bc2dadf53f7ff0ec1d71cc3a4b237037","tid":427390,"uid":75196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T01:14:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知有冇人一早已經知<br />\n話說今日自己一個食譚啦<br />\n食完譚仔先發現唔記得撳錢<br />\n埋單果時死死地氣咁問個收銀<br />\n可唔可以過隔離7仔撳畀你<br />\n佢話可以但你簽一簽呢張野先<br />\n<br />\n&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"https://holland.pk/ut8ghke3&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fut8ghke3%22&d=1MGcE3XRFIEMBMZtt5lJCy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=8e6a9c71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/ut8ghke3&quot;</a>  /&gt;<br />\n<br />\n我一望到成個人呆撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後面仲有兩三個人排緊隊等埋單<br />\n個個人望住我簽呢張回條 勁羞恥<br />\n到底邊個發明呢張野架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊個叫你唔撚帶錢？陣間出左去唔撚返黎，係咪叫阿姐自己墊番你條數？"},{"pid":"5da939564609bd27f7c28f4edb0ce08594e687a1","tid":427390,"uid":10345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T01:14:57.000Z","msg":"雲吞哥咁唔小心啊"},{"pid":"5171cdc852257e16cedd85d7028508eefaf5d0c3","tid":427390,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T01:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52cdfda2843b5b69d94f36486bec0822903de48","tid":427390,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T01:47:06.000Z","msg":"放底部手機做抵押咪唔洗簽囉"},{"pid":"d2ddbcefe0ac2cd87a71f10016b6fad48fe34b5a","tid":427390,"uid":72688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T01:52:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放底部手機做抵押咪唔洗簽囉</blockquote><br />\n第一次都係放低電話，橫掂有password，唔驚比人攞，同埋簽張嘢好柒。。。。<br />\n<br />\n第二次阿姐認得我叫我快啲撳錢"},{"pid":"6ac39e8e6cc3d61a9340e4e041d2560759b93dcc","tid":427390,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T01:59:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔知有冇人一早已經知<br />\n話說今日自己一個食譚啦<br />\n食完譚仔先發現唔記得撳錢<br />\n埋單果時死死地氣咁問個收銀<br />\n可唔可以過隔離7仔撳畀你<br />\n佢話可以但你簽一簽呢張野先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ut8ghke3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fut8ghke3&h=a2d040a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我一望到成個人呆撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後面仲有兩三個人排緊隊等埋單<br />\n個個人望住我簽呢張回條 勁羞恥<br />\n到底邊個發明呢張野架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">敝</span></span>公司呀on9仔</blockquote><br />\n屌 你唔講都冇發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n張野樓主名義寫, 叫譚仔貴公司有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一句已經係&ldquo;本人...&rdquo;"},{"pid":"fc7224ab1e20a1204b6c5b17489da5fce111ba82","tid":427390,"uid":127244,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T02:04:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴線. 呢間嘢係咪好多人走數?</blockquote><br />\n正常啦，通常都係香港嗰班底層生物先會去食依啲濕鳩味精湯水垃圾荷爾蒙肉碎米線<br />\n班折墮鬼面皮特厚⋯⋯咁經常發生依啲事就唔出奇<br />\n老實講呢啲垃圾請我都食唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算肚餓都唔會有胃口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係唔明你班味覺殘廢嘅垃圾例如樓主依類地底泥嘅垃圾父母點解仲要生育下一代出嚟遺禍人間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/no